divs: Sighting DetailsMy wife and I were outside shooting some digital images of the full moon 11:30 in the evening, using a Canon Powershot 6.0 megapixel with 48x zoom. I took four successive shots of the moon and this object appeared on the last shot. We were reviewing the images and saw this red 3 dimensional image. The size of this, whatever it is must be enormous. We went back out and looked again but were unable to see it.
Summary: Red diamond shape object appears on last image of 4 shots of a full moon
